title: FRIDAY - A thriller in Sin City 2020
itunes:title: FRIDAY - A thriller in Sin City 2020
description:
It was a wild shootout in Las Vegas (0:09) as the Chargers outlast the Raiders in overtime. We have the latest injury news on a pair of QBs as Drew Brees (1:30) and Alex Smith (2:14) still have a chance to play in week 15. Giants offensive coordinator Jason Garrett (2:33) testing positive for COVID-19, so New York will turn to a former Browns head coach to lead the way on Sunday. Plus, Aaron Rodgers talks (3:12) about his MVP chances against Patrick Mahomes
